Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.81,0:01:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just before Operation Odessa...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...the White Base was critically damaged\Nin combat, and made a crash landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.98,0:01:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Although the Zeon attack force\Nhad withdrawn for the time being...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...there was no telling\Nwhen they would attack again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.77,0:02:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Matilda's Rescue
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The one on the right should be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we use the cord for the engine No. 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the scale is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.99,0:02:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm running out of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai! Someone's going to call you\Na coward again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see what the pressure is here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.65,0:03:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we manage with what we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.\NWe've tried everything, but it's no go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. If the enemy attacked now, we'd be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We are getting supplies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We made a request to General Revil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ms. Mirai, Mr. Bright is calling for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ms. Mirai, Mr. Bright Is calling for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.09,0:03:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Bright?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to be my substitute.\NTake over for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A ship without a commander\Nseems pathetic. But... I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,None of us can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm filled with shame when I think\Nthat my fear may be what's making me ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.32,0:03:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are the basics of ship command.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you study this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But... that's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- I know you can do it.\N- Bright...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll do it, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, having received\Nthe White Base's resupply request...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...General Revil of the Federation Forces\Nhad arrived at the European frontline base.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This was so that Operation Odessa could\Nhappen before Rear Admiral Kycilia...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...sent reinforcements to M'Quve's base.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,However, prior to this offensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the attack is coming from\Njust one ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...if M'Quve is attacked from behind,\Nhe'll panic and make his move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But I understand they're badly damaged\Nafter M'Quve's attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This plan might work because\Nthey assume that, General Elran.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Matilda...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest depends on whether your squadron...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...can repair the White Base's engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, General Revil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how bad the damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, there's another item\NI want you to deliver to the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Though they'll probably resent\Nbeing the guinea pigs again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want them to do the testing\Nfor the Gundam's power-up mecha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam's...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the documentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,General Revil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you giving so much support\Nto a unit that hasn't been properly organized?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't use the regular military\Nfor experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is also the decision of General HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for informing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't know any details\Nabout the Gundam's power-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unfortunately, General Elran didn't have.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell Elran that he should restrain himself\Nin the Odessa offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the Federation is getting impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In this battle, the first to move will lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Clink. Take 3 Goufs with 3 Dodai YSs...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...and hit the Medea transport team.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Take escort fighters as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mirai.\N- What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A coded message from\NGeneral Revil just came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've deciphered it by computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll display it.\N- Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This Is Revil. My apologiest you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lieutenant Matilda Is delivering{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You must join Operation Odessa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've also sent alongdam.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure they will be quite useful in battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope the pilots will fight better with them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it? We don't even know\Nwhen Operation Odessa begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Ms. Matilda...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...I mean, Lieutenant Matilda...\Nwill give us the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what the new Gundam parts are?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it's something that'll make it easier\Nfor Amuro and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Detecting a formation at 11 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when we're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- Zeon?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There can't be that many people\Naware of our movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All units, prepare for anti-air combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Maintain current combat formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Send General Revil an SOS, just in case.\N- Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Transports weighed down by their cargo\Nare a piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Receiving an SOS from\Nthe Medea transport squadron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Medea?! What's the distance?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,180 km, northwest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:08:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without those supplies...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We need the Medea to come to us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla. We need to assist\Nthe Medea transport squadron.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Kai! Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please launch!\NWe're rescuing Matilda's squadron.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Matilda's in trouble...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- No! Wait, Sayla! Stop the launch!\N- Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Without the Core Fighters...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...the immobile White Base\Nwill be defenseless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If the enemy hits us then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, go to the Core Fighter!\NJob John and Hayato, to the Gunperry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Load the Gundam parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai, to the Guncannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If that made you angry, you can punish me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright left me in charge...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:10:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Matilda's transport squadron\Nis bringing us emergency supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. Sayla, you always flatter us.\NHere I go, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Gunperry, heading out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to pray that\Nthe enemy doesn't come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai. Why don't you\Ngo sit in the captain's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more relaxing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should have everyone\Non anti-aircraft watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Matilda.\NPlease hang on until I get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Matilda! No. 5's been hit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- No matter! Fly lower to the ground!\N- Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not touching Ms. Matilda,\Nor the supplies!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's a Core Fighter!\N- Very fast, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But is it a match for those\NZeon mobile suits, the Goufs...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dopps are no problem.\NBut where are the Goufs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Down! Down! Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:11:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one Gouf...! Next...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to get between the enemy\Nand the Medea, or I'll hit Ms. Matilda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Mr. Kai!\NI'm running out of ammo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do repairs...\NRepairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to do what you can\Nwhile there's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time to be reading that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true, Ryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you did it wasn't the smartest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But you taught us all by your example.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A person's value depends\Non what that person does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You were strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...that's why I want to be like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Make your own decisions...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...and take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, I'm entering the docking area!\NCan you make it here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I read you, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy aircraft at 5 o'clock!\NWe don't have data on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid. We've got\Nall the data on the Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it now! A splitting type!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A splitting type?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.09,0:14:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the one that carries\Nthe Gundam mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Habe, cease attack on the Medeas!\NWe're going after the splitting type!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Splitting type? What's that?!\NIs the mobile suit in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Have the remaining Dopps\Nchase the fighters away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! You're going to transfer\Nto the Gundam right here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to! The Core Fighter\Nisn't enough to defeat the Goufs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Activating laser searcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser searcher activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Synchronizing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A Gouf!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Get the fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy here's a bit slow, y'know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hurry up and do the Gundam thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! Give me cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There are Goufs around the Medea, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:14:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Docking searcher... activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,10... 9...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,6... 5...\NReleasing B Parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Searcher synchronized!\NReleasing A Parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Converting to a mobile suit, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Gouf! You'll pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that's not Ms. Matilda's!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. 1! No. 4 Is down!\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No. 4 has the Gundam's power-up mecha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to land the formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:16:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But our two aircraft can still get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't abandon the Gundam's\Npower-up mecha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They landed?!\NThis is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Is it that Gouf again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Get the G-Mecha unloaded!\NWe're going to blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up the anti-air fire!\NThere's one enemy mobile suit left!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:17:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Matilda's going to be hit\Nunless you get here quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I should probably\Ntry to shoot it down...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Power up the G-Fighter's engines.\NWe'll have the Gundam use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You think he'll learn to use it that quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What does a commander do at time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.87,0:17:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Mirai, at times like this, we feel safe\Nwhen a commander looks calm and confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No enemies closing in, are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No sign of any. The Medea transports\Nseem to be stalled as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Sayla, can you inform\Nthe mechanics?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancel level 1 battle stations\Nand resume repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the enemy doesn't have\Nmuch fighting strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's taking them so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine. They won't come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Gouf! Seems to be\Ngetting stronger and stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he finished?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He got me! My engine...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! My leg circuits are all shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to get to Ms. Matilda, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:19:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai, has Matilda's squadron arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's fine.\NThey say they should be here in 5 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. They got through\Nthe Zeon siege, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's why they made her\Na First Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... I'd like to rest some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't move freely!\NWhat to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, I'll be over-powered!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this it...?!\NNo, you're not going to get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:20:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the power-up mecha\NMs. Matilda brought!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We can put the Gundam on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...! Let's try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go, Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost too much power already!\NI'm taking you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.31,0:20:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato! Ram him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato! Turn! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The G-Fighter...\NSo that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I got the report.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.42,0:21:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ms. Mirai. As acting commander, well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.09,0:21:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd like you now touadron...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.55,0:21:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and expedite repairs to the White Base.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel more and more ashamed of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't, Mirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.70,0:21:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You held on well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And you were able\Nto put Bright at ease, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.58,0:22:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sayla.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It means a lot to me,\Ncoming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With all this, the White Base\Nwill be fixed up in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.25,0:22:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the second time\NI've been saved by you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.68,0:22:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...Amuro and Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.03,0:22:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And Kai too. Today must have\Nbeen the toughest on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... That was nothing, really...\NPractically a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're so dependable, Kai.\N- Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.35,0:22:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's have you take a look\Nat all the new Gundam power-up parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.66,0:22:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.33,0:22:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm going to try even harder\Nand get even better...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.21,0:22:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.01,0:22:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.37,0:23:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Matilda dies protecting\Nthe White Base...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.59,0:23:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...along with many of her brave comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dom heavy mobile suits,\Nnicknamed the Black Tri-Stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...make for an unrelenting\Nshow of ferocity.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.30,0:23:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...\NBlack Tri-Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.84,0:23:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Black Tri-Star
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.76,0:23:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.19,0:23:54.03,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:59.03,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.03,0:24:09.25,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.25,0:24:14.18,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:18.81,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.81,0:24:24.19,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.19,0:24:28.77,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.77,0:24:39.08,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.19,0:23:54.03,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:59.03,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.03,0:24:09.25,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.25,0:24:14.18,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:18.81,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.81,0:24:24.19,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.19,0:24:28.77,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.77,0:24:39.08,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
